{"tid":632893,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局於紐約尾市兩度掃入港元　涉逾51億（第9～10）","createTime":"2018-04-17T22:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T00:37:22.000Z","uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f861b5c304ed267c88854d2ca53535200cd9a8","tid":632893,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T22:41:07.000Z","msg":"港匯續弱！由於港元兌每美元再度觸及7.85的弱方兌換保證水平，香港金融管理局在紐約時段周二尾市(香港時間周三凌晨5時左右)，一小時內兩度掃入港元來捍衛聯匯，先後分別買入15.7億和35.33億港元，共涉51.03億港元。 <br />\n<br />\n金管局日內已經4度出手買入港元，令購買港元的規模增至146.8億港元。 <br />\n<br />\n自上周四起，金管局已經至少10次買入港元，累積涉資約337億港元，令4月19日的銀行體系結餘降至1,461.51億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180418/mobile/bkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180418%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001.html&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74Pgzmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6f19980b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180418/mobile/bkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dc6eb769895ac584ef78454431d499de0ca16194","tid":632893,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T22:43:06.000Z","msg":"1日150億<br />\n<br />\n資金極速流走，好多人聞風即逃"},{"pid":"799ea280d5752bfc1fc04454446c0fb6775074c5","tid":632893,"uid":129507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T22:50:40.000Z","msg":"沽呀沽"},{"pid":"35655f130efacf351614d889bd89a87c262db254","tid":632893,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T22:51:10.000Z","msg":"10個交易日 用完<br />\n加息<br />\n但港元信心無問題<br />\n拆息升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1d71efad291c84f4857163ffdfd55200806860","tid":632893,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35655f130efacf351614d889bd89a87c262db254","tid":632893,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T22:51:10.000